{"tid":795381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家仲有冇人講奶冚？","createTime":"2018-08-27T03:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T11:07:55.000Z","uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"09f25ebb89ffdc2b72e58c4089d58bb0975f8517","tid":795381,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"以前好多人講<br />\n因為興同型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家好多人都講bra同埋胸圍<br />\n完全唔型加冇霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奶冚就唔同<br />\n一講出黎d人就feel到個陣霸氣<br />\n而且，男朋友唔洗再驚幫女朋友買奶冚<br />\n因為當你同個職員講要奶冚<br />\n而唔係講bra 胸圍<br />\n個職員就員同周圍d人就知你咩料<br />\n唔會再暗中閒言閒語<br />\n而係產生敬畏<br />\n所以從今日起我地要講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">奶冚</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6e5578cebb4d4dcce2784a9ac2e000d1c1c413","tid":795381,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"薄lock"},{"pid":"9b4dfb405ba069d6d39601dba1f8cf4c2bf23e0e","tid":795381,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b6e5578cebb4d4dcce2784a9ac2e000d1c1c413","tid":795381,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"薄lock"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:32:39.000Z","msg":"都係唔夠奶冚霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa04090511002d1a78a837f19269a0bc6c61a44","tid":795381,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:34:36.000Z","msg":"睇黎連登仔都係講開bra同胸圍<br />\n好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ebab3f7e0593b6238d03600b2d4b14f1dc9016","tid":795381,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"真係冇人講奶冚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c6cf2ead2e327addc2338fc